### 1. Get Order Details
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get Payment Details for Order
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/orders/{{orderId}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Create Payment Redirect (Midtrans)
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/orders/{{orderId}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": "credit_card"
}

### 4. Cancel Order
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/orders/{{orderId}}/cancellations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Changed my mind"
}
